                <note rend="inline" type="source">851.01/2283: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to the
                        Consul General at Algiers</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Wiley</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1943-06-17">June 17,
                            1943</date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>1147. For Murphy. Your telegram, June 16th.<note n="56" xml:id="d126fn56"
                        >Telegram No. 1108, <ref target="#pg_152">p. 152</ref>.</note> Approve your
                    suggestion contained in paragraph third before end. Will telegraph again.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Hull</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
